# Force hoisting of bundler-time deps that pnpm's default isolation leaves
# unreachable to Metro / @babel/core / react-native-reanimated scripts.
#
# Why each one:
#   yallist · hoisted lru-cache@5.1.1 (transitive of @babel/core) does
#            `require('yallist')` from .pnpm/node_modules/lru-cache/. Combined
#            with the workspace override pinning yallist to v4 (CJS class
#            export), this guarantees the sibling is present.
#   semver  · react-native-reanimated's validate-worklets-version.js does
#            `require('semver/functions/satisfies')`. The default-hoisted
#            semver@6 doesn't expose the subpath; we need semver@7+ next to it.
#   getenv  · @expo/cli's bin script requires it from its own location, which
#            on pnpm resolves up to .pnpm/node_modules/.
#
# hoist-pattern[]        → places packages in node_modules/.pnpm/node_modules/
#                          (where the bundler-side require() sites look)
# public-hoist-pattern[] → places packages in top-level node_modules/
#                          (where direct require('...') from project code looks)
# Both are set because the require() chain crosses between layers.
hoist-pattern[]=yallist
hoist-pattern[]=semver
hoist-pattern[]=getenv
public-hoist-pattern[]=yallist
public-hoist-pattern[]=semver
public-hoist-pattern[]=getenv
